      "content": "idk i just feel like i dont even exist anymore. i work from home, the apartment is always quiet, and i spend all day just staring at a screen. if i just stopped logging on or stopped showing up, i dont think i think anyone would even notice. like i'm just a ghost in the machine or something.",
